00:26:04,050 --> 00:26:06,980
and as the next king of Madelin.

247
00:26:09,200 --> 00:26:10,200
Yes, Fath.

248
00:26:13,710 --> 00:26:16,610
[Thailand]

249
00:27:20,130 --> 00:27:24,710
I am Police General Wathit
Watinwanich, Your Highness.

250
00:27:47,700 --> 00:27:49,130
This way please, Your Highness.

251
00:28:10,530 --> 00:28:17,280
This is a team of skilled female officers
carefully selected to provide security…

252
00:28:18,100 --> 00:28:21,400
During your stay in
Thailand, Your Highness.

253
00:29:04,060 --> 00:29:11,700
This one is Police Lieutenant Vayo Watinwanich,
head of the security team, Your Highness.

254
00:29:15,660 --> 00:29:22,360
I solemnly vow that my team and I shall protect Princess
Catherine to the best of our abilities, Your Highness.

255
00:29:24,960 --> 00:29:31,400
Thank you. If you need anything, you can
talk to Grace. She is my trusted servant.

256
00:30:09,000 --> 00:30:11,580
Aww, Lom.

257
00:30:12,610 --> 00:30:14,650
You hardly blinked there.

258
00:30:14,930 --> 00:30:15,930
What?

259
00:30:16,100 --> 00:30:21,200
Princess Blew. I saw it. You were
looking at her without batting an eye.

260
00:30:22,000 --> 00:30:23,706
Are you hoping for
someone out of your league?

261
00:30:23,730 --> 00:30:24,730
Nonsense.

262
00:30:25,460 --> 00:30:26,460
That's the princess.

263
00:30:26,860 --> 00:30:29,676
What if someone hears us, we'll surely
get our asses kicked for royal defamation.

264
00:30:29,700 --> 00:30:31,160
Geez, don't get so serious.

265
00:30:31,560 --> 00:30:32,360
I was only teasing.

266
00:30:32,530 --> 00:30:33,530
You can't.

267
00:30:33,760 --> 00:30:35,800
It's already wrong to even think about it.

268
00:30:38,730 --> 00:30:40,750
- Not even a thought?
- Yeah.

269
00:30:40,960 --> 00:30:43,460
Let's go get ready. The princess
will visit many places today.

270
00:32:17,730 --> 00:32:20,836
This temple is very ancient and sacred.

271
00:32:20,860 --> 00:32:22,850
Thai people love to
come here to make a wish.

272
00:32:29,730 --> 00:32:32,360
Then, can I make a wish too?

273
00:32:34,360 --> 00:32:35,360
Of course, Your Highness.

274
00:33:05,800 --> 00:33:07,300
Please put it on the tray.

275
00:33:21,060 --> 00:33:23,960
Then, bow and pay respect three time.

276
00:33:26,600 --> 00:33:27,710
Pay respect?

277
00:34:22,480 --> 00:34:27,080
[Wangna Theater] / [Wangna Arts Gallery]

278
00:34:34,659 --> 00:34:42,659
Displayed on this side are artworks of Professor Pichai Nirand,
the national artist in visual arts (painting) for the year 2003.

279
00:34:45,409 --> 00:34:50,456
He is known for his modern traditional
oil paintings that feature Thai culture.

280
00:34:50,480 --> 00:34:54,256
Or what most people
call 'modern traditional'.

281
00:34:54,280 --> 00:34:59,186
If you look carefully, you will see that most
of his paintings also feature lotus flowers

282
00:34:59,210 --> 00:35:03,680
as well as the Buddha's footprint
to signify peacefulness in Buddhism.

283
00:35:04,080 --> 00:35:09,886
As for his choices of colours, they are vivid
yet able to convey the gentle nature of reality.

284
00:35:09,910 --> 00:35:12,050
Let's move over to that
side, Your Highness.

285
00:35:59,300 --> 00:36:00,800
My apologies, Your Highness.

286
00:36:04,060 --> 00:36:05,060
Thank you.

287
00:36:10,700 --> 00:36:12,300
Is there something wrong, Your Highness?

288
00:36:26,680 --> 00:36:31,080
[Traditional instrumental music]

289
00:36:59,360 --> 00:37:03,826
Our intelligence unit has just informed me
about a treasonist's attempt to assassinate you…

290
00:37:03,850 --> 00:37:08,010
Due to their disapproval of your
recent title as the heir apparent.

291
00:37:12,960 --> 00:37:18,510
As I thought, the situation there is
eerily calm and disturbingly peaceful.

292
00:37:19,330 --> 00:37:23,480
Now that I'm also away from Madelin, it
gives those treasonists more opportunities.

293
00:37:28,060 --> 00:37:31,680
Will you inform your father, Your Highness?

294
00:37:33,800 --> 00:37:41,800
I don't want to worry him. At least, the government here
has already sent the police to provide more security.

295
00:37:51,060 --> 00:37:54,180
Do you think we can trust them?

296
00:37:57,100 --> 00:38:02,650
I don't know. But at the moment,
I don't think we can trust anyone.

297
00:38:03,010 --> 00:38:05,550
Not even people from Madelin.

298
00:38:09,860 --> 00:38:11,160
Please worry not, Your Highness.

299
00:38:13,400 --> 00:38:16,900
You still have me and Henri to protect you.

300
00:38:22,130 --> 00:38:25,300
Thank you so much, Grace,
for always staying beside me.

301
00:38:29,560 --> 00:38:32,306
Now, if you'll excuse me, Your Highness.
I need to check if everything is in order.

302
00:38:32,330 --> 00:38:37,750
[Rhythmic chanting of Thai ballards]

303
00:39:00,900 --> 00:39:02,960
You hardly take your eyes off of her, Lom.

304
00:39:03,930 --> 00:39:06,760
I'm here to protect the princess.
How could I take my eyes off of her?

305
00:39:08,530 --> 00:39:12,426
I'm not saying you should. Well then, just…

306
00:39:12,450 --> 00:39:16,450
Keep watching. I'll go to the loo first.

307
00:39:17,360 --> 00:39:20,550
- Keep watching. Don't let her out of your sight.
- Mhm.

308
00:39:55,660 --> 00:39:59,900
Grace, I want to exercise. Can you
make sure it's all clear at the gym?

309
00:40:00,860 --> 00:40:03,220
[Grace]: Yes, Your Highness.
I will attend to it right away.

310
00:40:55,530 --> 00:40:57,450
[Grace]: What are you doing, Lieutenant?

311
00:40:59,930 --> 00:41:01,810
I heard a glass shattering.

312
00:41:02,060 --> 00:41:04,200
Can I go inside to check
if everything is all right?

313
00:41:05,860 --> 00:41:07,360
Let me do it instead.

314
00:41:07,930 --> 00:41:10,750
The princess probably doesn't want
anyone to enter her room at night.

315
00:41:11,800 --> 00:41:17,810
But as the head of security, it is my
duty to make sure the princess is safe.

316
00:41:28,330 --> 00:41:29,330
What's the commotion?

317
00:41:30,530 --> 00:41:35,550
My apologies, Your Highness.
Are you hurt anywhere?

318
00:41:36,200 --> 00:41:37,480
I'm fine.

319
00:41:45,600 --> 00:41:47,960
Tell your team to withdraw from this floor.

320
00:41:49,730 --> 00:41:51,900
Our people from Madelin
will take charge instead.

321
00:41:52,860 --> 00:41:56,000
The princess does not
wish to be disturbed at night.

322
00:42:10,360 --> 00:42:11,930
Is everything all right?

323
00:42:13,560 --> 00:42:14,700
Yes, all good.

324
00:42:16,800 --> 00:42:17,800
What's wrong?

325
00:42:18,130 --> 00:42:20,100
Did something happen to the princess?

326
00:42:20,760 --> 00:42:22,400
No, the princess is safe.

327
00:42:23,660 --> 00:42:25,330
Then, why are you looking so serious?

328
00:42:28,330 --> 00:42:29,330
Nothing.

329
00:42:30,660 --> 00:42:33,306
Madelin's people will come to
take charge of this floor from now on.

330
00:42:33,330 --> 00:42:35,000
Let's move to point B instead.

331
00:42:37,000 --> 00:42:38,600
Stay on guard. I'll be right back.

332
00:42:38,900 --> 00:42:39,960
Where are you going?

333
00:42:42,160 --> 00:42:43,660
I'm sensing something fishy here.

334
00:42:44,360 --> 00:42:46,660
I'll do a round of
inspection just to make sure.

335
00:43:06,800 --> 00:43:09,660
You can leave. We'll take care of it here.

336
00:43:11,330 --> 00:43:13,350
Yes. Let's go.

337
00:44:08,560 --> 00:44:09,700
Is this the princess?

338
00:44:13,060 --> 00:44:14,060
So pretty.

339
00:44:14,260 --> 00:44:15,260
Yeah.

340
00:44:23,460 --> 00:44:26,580
[Helena]: How long are you going to
dote on her? Hurry up and take care of it.

341
00:44:36,530 --> 00:44:37,530
Wow, exactly the same.

342
00:44:45,700 --> 00:44:48,700
Cover up her face so that
no one will recognise her.

343
00:44:53,150 --> 00:44:54,400
Okay. Give me a hand.

344
00:45:30,160 --> 00:45:31,160
Take her inside.

345
00:45:34,750 --> 00:45:35,880
Quick!

346
00:45:47,400 --> 00:45:49,300
Keep watch. I'll be back.

347
00:46:17,530 --> 00:46:18,550
Kill her.

348
00:46:21,060 --> 00:46:23,700
Don't leave any traces of evidence.

349
00:46:26,960 --> 00:46:31,110
Kill the princess? That's a national crime!

350
00:46:32,560 --> 00:46:34,160
Are you sure it will be okay?

351
00:46:34,930 --> 00:46:36,060
Don't worry.

352
00:46:37,760 --> 00:46:40,560
Everyone thinks Princess
Blew is still in her room.

353
00:46:41,730 --> 00:46:42,960
No one would suspect anything.

354
00:46:45,000 --> 00:46:49,000
You and your men'd better not mess it up.

355
00:47:32,200 --> 00:47:35,180
Go check the princess in
case she might wake up.

356
00:47:35,330 --> 00:47:37,600
She's been drugged.
She won't wake up so fast.

357
00:47:38,860 --> 00:47:39,960
Just do as I said.

358
00:47:41,960 --> 00:47:44,450
Hey! Go check on her.

359
00:48:28,510 --> 00:48:29,510
Stop!

360
00:48:33,500 --> 00:48:36,726
Help! Help!

361
00:48:36,750 --> 00:48:37,187
Hey! Stop!

362
00:48:37,211 --> 00:48:38,380
Help!

363
00:48:38,600 --> 00:48:40,130
Stop or I'll shoot!

364
00:48:44,160 --> 00:48:46,810
Help! Help.

365
00:48:54,160 --> 00:48:56,350
Help! Help!

366
00:48:58,130 --> 00:48:59,810
Help! Help!

367
00:49:00,000 --> 00:49:01,110
Help!

368
00:49:02,760 --> 00:49:05,250
Where do you think you're going, Princess?

369
00:49:10,160 --> 00:49:13,450
Do you wanna die that much, huh?!

370
00:49:23,310 --> 00:49:24,380
[Gunshot]

371
00:49:52,500 --> 00:49:53,500
Who the f♪♪♪ are you?

372
00:49:59,530 --> 00:50:00,530
Put your gun down.

373
00:50:12,880 --> 00:50:13,880
Damn it!

374
00:50:38,680 --> 00:50:40,880
[Gunshots]

375
00:50:54,600 --> 00:50:59,160
My car is downstairs.
Come with me. Let's go!

376
00:51:06,210 --> 00:51:07,210
Get in the car.

377
00:51:26,400 --> 00:51:27,400
F♪♪♪!

378
00:51:39,200 --> 00:51:40,380
Go after them, Khem.

379
00:52:26,130 --> 00:52:27,330
Suae, there she is!

380
00:52:27,800 --> 00:52:29,060
Good! Go faster.

381
00:52:48,600 --> 00:52:50,060
Don't let them out of sight!

382
00:53:47,980 --> 00:53:49,580
- Hey! F♪♪♪ off!
- Damn it!

383
00:53:56,960 --> 00:53:58,500
We've lost them.

384
00:54:03,300 --> 00:54:04,300
Miss?

385
00:54:07,330 --> 00:54:08,330
Are you all right?

386
00:54:10,500 --> 00:54:11,500
Miss.

387
00:54:28,130 --> 00:54:31,480
Miss.

388
00:54:33,000 --> 00:54:37,310
Miss! Are you hurt anywhere?

389
00:54:38,700 --> 00:54:39,700
Miss!

390
00:54:49,460 --> 00:54:50,460
Princess!

391
00:55:00,350 --> 00:55:05,280
Miss Vayo, please help me.

392
00:55:14,310 --> 00:55:18,250
[Rada Clinic]

393
00:55:39,000 --> 00:55:40,060
How's she doing?

394
00:55:41,100 --> 00:55:44,726
The patient has been exposed to a poison that affects
her nervous system. That's why she passed out.

395
00:55:44,750 --> 00:55:47,830
I'm waiting for her blood result. Then,
we'll know what kind of poison it is.

396
00:55:48,730 --> 00:55:50,260
It's not critical, isn't it?

397
00:55:50,760 --> 00:55:54,160
Mhm. She's safe now. You just
have to wait for her to recover.

398
00:55:55,660 --> 00:55:56,660
Thanks a lot.

399
00:56:00,050 --> 00:56:03,730
So, what on earth got
her poisoned like this?

400
00:56:05,300 --> 00:56:09,100
Don't tell me even a pro
like you needs to drug a girl.

401
00:56:10,860 --> 00:56:12,086
What kind of person do you think I am?

402
00:56:12,110 --> 00:56:15,280
I accidentally came across
her while I was on duty.

403
00:56:16,700 --> 00:56:18,140
I thought she's your new girlfriend.

404
00:56:19,660 --> 00:56:22,930
I'm not that stupid to bring my
new GF to get treatment from my ex.

405
00:56:24,300 --> 00:56:25,300
If you say so.

406
00:56:28,160 --> 00:56:34,110
By the way, she looks so familiar. But
I'm not sure where I've seen her before.

407
00:56:35,130 --> 00:56:37,500
You're a doctor not a reporter.
Why are you so curious?

408
00:56:38,400 --> 00:56:40,586
Of course, I have to ask.

409
00:56:40,610 --> 00:56:44,850
What if the patient you bring is a
prisoner, wouldn't I be in trouble too?

410
00:56:45,730 --> 00:56:50,330
I already feel unlucky seeing you today.

411
00:56:51,360 --> 00:56:53,760
Aww, Babe.

412
00:56:55,300 --> 00:57:01,360
What babe? Should I just bash your brain
in? I never forget what you did to me.

413
00:57:05,110 --> 00:57:07,310
[Phone ringing]

414
00:57:08,800 --> 00:57:09,800
Just a sec.

415
00:57:14,130 --> 00:57:15,130
Yeah?

416
00:57:15,560 --> 00:57:18,580
Lom! Where are you?

417
00:57:18,800 --> 00:57:20,930
There was a shooting behind the hotel!

418
00:57:21,260 --> 00:57:24,500
I heard it's the Madelin terrorists
who are lurking in Thailand in disguise.

419
00:57:26,000 --> 00:57:28,760
Chief is completely flipped out
because he can't find you here.

420
00:57:30,760 --> 00:57:32,730
What about Princess Catherine?

421
00:57:37,130 --> 00:57:38,460
She's safe now.

422
00:57:39,700 --> 00:57:41,200
She's resting inside.

423
00:57:57,500 --> 00:57:59,300
Are you sure the princess is at the hotel?

424
00:58:01,800 --> 00:58:02,960
Are you sure she's safe?

425
00:58:04,330 --> 00:58:05,760
Did you see her with your own eyes?

426
00:58:07,160 --> 00:58:10,950
Yes! She even asked for your
presence tomorrow morning.

427
00:58:17,600 --> 00:58:19,660
I got it now. Thanks a lot.

428
00:58:49,560 --> 00:58:51,400
Miss Vayo is here, Your Highness.

429
00:58:54,900 --> 00:58:56,100
Greetings, Your Highness.

430
00:58:58,460 --> 00:59:02,560
You can drop the formality. And
don't use royal vocabs with me.

431
00:59:03,730 --> 00:59:07,100
I just want to ask about
the incident last night.

432
00:59:08,530 --> 00:59:11,300
What is it that you would like
to know, Princess Catherine?

433
00:59:14,300 --> 00:59:20,450
Grace, go out first. I want
to talk to Miss Vayo alone.

434
00:59:21,210 --> 00:59:22,280
Yes, Your Highness.

435
00:59:39,260 --> 00:59:47,260
There was an unexpected incident last night. But how
come you as the head of security was nowhere to be seen?

436
00:59:49,460 --> 00:59:51,500
I had an urgent matter to
attend to, Your Highness.

437
00:59:52,000 --> 00:59:54,530
Is that matter more
important than my safety?

438
00:59:56,930 --> 00:59:58,700
My deepest apologies, Your Highness.

439
00:59:59,860 --> 01:00:05,650
As the head of security, I am solely
responsible for this absence from duty.

440
01:00:06,930 --> 01:00:09,810
But please pardon your punishment
on the rest of my team, Your Highness.

441
01:00:12,700 --> 01:00:14,500
I won't punish you, Miss Vayo.

442
01:00:15,560 --> 01:00:18,760
The incident was sudden and unexpected.

443
01:00:20,300 --> 01:00:25,310
But after this, I do hope
it won't happen again.

444
01:00:29,300 --> 01:00:32,560
I promise that I will do
my best to keep you safe,

445
01:00:33,700 --> 01:00:35,360
even if I have to sacrifice my own life.

446
01:00:37,130 --> 01:00:38,160
I appreciate it.

447
01:01:08,010 --> 01:01:12,780
[Princess Blew]: Miss Vayo, please help me.

448
01:01:21,130 --> 01:01:24,556
[Next Episode] What happened,
Lom? Why were you absent on duty?

449
01:01:24,580 --> 01:01:26,580
Why disappear and
abandon your team like that?

450
01:01:26,930 --> 01:01:28,460
Who told you this, Dad?

451
01:01:28,600 --> 01:01:31,330
Henri, Madelin's royal guard.

452
01:01:31,860 --> 01:01:34,130
Impossible! How come no
one knows I've been missing?

453
01:01:35,160 --> 01:01:39,000
Because right now there's an imposter
taking your place as Princess Blew.

454
01:01:39,530 --> 01:01:42,486
If what Grace has right now is the
fake princess who looks like me…

455
01:01:42,510 --> 01:01:45,056
And also the family heirloom,

456
01:01:45,080 --> 01:01:49,110
There's almost no way to
prove I'm the real princess.

457
01:01:49,560 --> 01:01:51,350
But you still have me, Miss Blew.

458
01:02:04,310 --> 01:02:08,756
♫ From now on, my heart and soul
will be yours for the rest of my life ♫

459
01:02:08,780 --> 01:02:12,050
♫ Always have each other, never let go ♫

460
01:02:12,810 --> 01:02:17,226
♫ Trust in me 'cause I'll be by your side ♫

461
01:02:17,250 --> 01:02:22,310
♫ Hold my hand, Baby ♫

